# UX & Accessibility Standards

Follow the canonical standard: **`.ai/standards/ux-accessibility.md`**

Key rules:
- WCAG 2.2 AA: contrast, keyboard navigation, visible focus, ARIA, prefers-reduced-motion
- Specify loading, empty, error, and success states for every screen
- Mobile-first and responsive; reflow without horizontal scroll at 320px
- Reuse design-system tokens before adding new values

